{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ecf33c0d10","title":"中共北京市委关于制止一切打死人现象的紧急通知（概要）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"40b213a375","index":0,"year":1966,"month":9,"day":2,"articleId":"ecf33c0d10"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3bff1d2fc6","name":"暴力和武斗","type":"主题"},{"id":"ef6e778547","name":"中央文件","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"fd5220d4e9","name":"北京市发文件","type":"发行机构"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"46e2be23ca","type":"title","text":"中共北京市委关于制止一切打死人现象的紧急通知（概要）","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ecf33c0d10"},{"id":"5979d9d912","type":"paragraph","text":"1966年9月2日，北京市委发出《紧急通知》：指出“要用最大努力耐心说服和坚决制止一切打死人的现象。”从现在起一律禁止提供所谓流氓分子名单，违者要受纪律处分。除现行犯外，五类分子的名单，也不要向群众提供。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ecf33c0d10"}],"page":{"id":"a89b938128","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ecf33c0d10","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}